    <item>
      <title>CVS 再次下调预期，启动 20 亿美元成本削减计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/cvs-slashes-outlook-again-launches-2-billion-cost-cutting-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于医疗费用持续飙升，CVS Health Corp. 连续第三个季度下调了 2024 年盈利预期，并宣布了削减成本的措施，以在几年内节省 20 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/cvs-slashes-outlook-again-launches-2-billion-cost-cutting-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Implats 预计将因 10 亿美元减记而亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/implats-takes-1-billion-writedown-to-report-loss-on-price-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英帕拉铂金控股有限公司 (Impala Platinum Holdings Ltd.) 表示，其即将公布的财务业绩将包括 198 亿兰特（10.8 亿美元）的减值，并警告称，在铂族金属价格回落后，该公司将转为全年亏损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/implats-takes-1-billion-writedown-to-report-loss-on-price-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:21:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lyft 预订量和前景不及预期，股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/lyft-shares-slide-after-bookings-and-outlook-miss-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在该叫车公司公布第二季度预订量并发布低于华尔街预期的前景后，来福车公司 (Lyft Inc.) 的股价出现一年多来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/lyft-shares-slide-after-bookings-and-outlook-miss-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:06:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴尔的摩电费明年将上涨 11%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/baltimore-home-power-bills-to-jump-11-next-year-as-costs-soar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月的电网拍卖中，采购电力的成本飙升至历史最高水平，巴尔的摩地区的房主很可能会看到电费从 2025 年中期开始上涨 11%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/baltimore-home-power-bills-to-jump-11-next-year-as-costs-soar</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 23:11:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：日本央行鸽派信号推动全球股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，日本意外加息在一定程度上引发了历史性的市场动荡，日本央行采取措施安抚市场后，全球股市上涨，债券市场下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 22:38:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Airbnb 股价因前景不佳和预订量下降而创下历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/airbnb-gives-soft-outlook-on-signs-of-slowing-demand-from-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在该公司发布又一份令人失望的前景并警告美国度假者的需求放缓后，Airbnb Inc. 股价盘中创下历史新低。]]></description>
